text: Chanel Terrero Mart√≠nez, (born 28 July 1991) is a Cuban-Spanish singer, dancer and theatre actress from Havana. In 2022, she won the first edition of the Benidorm Fest, earning her the right to represent Spain in the Eurovision Song Contest 2022 in Turin.
